<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">سمع:</span> عَمْرو بن معد يكرب.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">سمع مِنْهُ:</span> جَعْفَر بن ربيعَة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَالَ ذَلِك البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَالثَّانِي:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢٧٣]</span> عبد الله بن أبي رَافع.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي هـ هُرَيْرَة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْن أبي ذِئْب.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عبد الله بن ربيعَة، وَعبد الله بن أبي ربيعَة<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">الأول:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>جمَاعَة يكون عَددهمْ سَبْعَة رجال، ذَكَرْنَاهُمْ فِي كتاب <span class="c2">((الْمُتَّفق والمفترق)</span>) .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>